    <section name="Type in editing region">
      <span class="shortdesc">How to type in an editing regin, creating markuped text.</span>

   <script type="text/javascript">
    leftpx=450;
    bottompx=350;
   </script>
   <div class='group'> 
    <div id='screenshot'><div>
     <img src="../../../../images/editing_region.png" alt='Editing region screenshot'/>
   </div></div></div>

   <p>
    In any editing region you can create markuped text, i.e.: You can make some text boldface,
    italic or underlined. You can make indented lists of numbered or bulleted items. You can make
    tables. And you can add images and web links.
    If you need more room for typing, you can maximize the editing region. All these functions
    are invoked by a button on the topline of the editing region.
    When done <a href='./save_settings.html'>save the settings</a>.
   </p>

